Install Screen.

sudo apt install screen
or
sudo pacman -S screen

Chmod.

sudo chmod 777 resw
sudo chmod 777 resa
sudo chmod 777 sa
sudo chmod 777 sw

Start Emulator.

sudo sh ./sa
sudo sh ./sw

Look Screen Console, Type:

sudo screen -r auth
sudo screen -r world

To Unlook Screen - no crash server, type:

Ctrl+A+D